name: Rise Of The Dark Lord
Text: 'Deploy on table (deploys only at start of game) with three different [Vader] Effects from your Reserve Deck face down under here.  Once per turn, may deploy a [Vader] Effect from here (never from elsewhere).  Limit one [Vader] Effect on table and, when lost, stack it under here.  You may cancel your [Vader] Effect at any time.Twisted And Evil: Dark Jedi Presence, Jedi Presence, Revenge Of The Sith and Sith Tests are canceled.  When using The Empire''s Back to deploy Vader from Reserve Deck, it is a Used Interrupt.  If you just drew a [Vader] card for destiny, may take it into hand.',
